    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241270/extras/000330a9a9251d989e3c2a00287a23b7.poster.avif?t=1764424883\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241270/extras/000330a9a9251d989e3c2a00287a23b7.webm?t=1764424883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241270/extras/000330a9a9251d989e3c2a00287a23b7.mp4?t=1764424883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[关于]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Into the Void》是一款快节奏的复古第一人称射击游戏，灵感来自《Post Void》和《ULTRAKILL》等肾上腺素飙升的游戏体验。它具有高速动作、激烈战斗，以及大胆玩法带来的刺激感，并拥有独特鲜明的艺术风格。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241270/extras/fc8d937c32df9e38b414df2d0ac4589c.poster.avif?t=1764424883\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241270/extras/fc8d937c32df9e38b414df2d0ac4589c.webm?t=1764424883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241270/extras/fc8d937c32df9e38b414df2d0ac4589c.mp4?t=1764424883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[特色]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 干净流畅的快节奏游戏体验   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 独特的武器与生命系统，搭配多样的移动技巧和强化道具，突破速度极限   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 风格化的黑白美术风格 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241270/extras/